comments: Lowry (TOR) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Ross' (ORL) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Gordon (ORL) places a hand/arm to the front of Leonard (TOR) during the drive but the contact is marginal.
Fournier (ORL) gets his hand on the ball during Leonard's (TOR) drive to the basket and a held ball should be called.
Siakam (TOR) makes contact with Fournier (ORL) during his driving shot attempt but the contact is marginal.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position from a wide stance and makes leg to leg contact with Leonard (TOR).
Siakam (TOR) jumps vertically and makes incidental contact with Augustin (ORL) at the end of his drive.
LAR shows Green (TOR) makes contact to the arm of Vucevic (ORL) that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Fournier (ORL) wraps Siakam (TOR) and affects his ability to get to the pass.
Siakam (TOR) makes marginal contact with Fournier (ORL) attempting to establish post position.
Leonard (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Vucevic (ORL).
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Green (TOR) and gives him space to avoid the contact.
Vucevic (ORL) firms up in a screening position in Leonard's (TOR) path and does not deliver contact.
Gordon (ORL) allows Leonard (TOR) to land safely following his jump shot attempt.
Lowry (TOR) makes incidental contact with Augustin (ORL) going for the rebound.
Gordon (ORL) makes contact to the arm of Leonard (TOR) before the start of his shooting motion.
Siakam (TOR) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Ross (ORL).
Green (TOR) makes marginal contact to Vucevic (TOR) and does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Vucevic (ORL) makes clean contact to the ball and any contact to VanVleet (ORL) is considered incidental.
Gordon (ORL) throws the ball out of bounds.
